{"tid":1424545,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭的復仇行動：上綱上線打港獨","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:11:16.000Z","uid":255637,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c485fbf0a1322de2223ed47f40068464dc6374","tid":1424545,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:03:31.000Z","msg":"希望大家聽聽  你話我P牌仔又好 分化狗又好 我都要講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林奠點解龜縮左成個月  但就係擇係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">8月5號</span></strong> 三罷呢一日搞記者會<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係因為佢驚我地 而係佢諗到方法去反擊我地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.  每日黑警記者會同跨部門記者會去分化我地<br />\n2.  透過不合作運動去令到人民鬥人民 將焦點由示威者對政府 改為黃絲鬥藍絲 同2014年一樣<br />\n3.  派出黑幫去攻擊我地   荃灣 北角 元朗有曬實證俾你睇 而差佬係絕對唔會理同拉人 <br />\n4.  你見佢成個記者會係重申 送中條例已完結 係有某部份人想搞事 打著光復香港 時代革命既口號 要打擊香港作為世界金融城市既地位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要記住 佢全個記者會都唔係講緊俾勇武派同和理非聽 佢係專注當日無出黎既500萬香港市民聽</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我相信黑警既武力會不斷升級 黑社會攻擊我地既次數亦會更加嚴重 <br />\n無可否認既係 不間斷既遊行同集會 即管係和平都好 黑警都會挑起事端 最後被暴力清場 <br />\n<br />\n而勇武既成效亦一次比一次低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6.12 我地靠勇武 推停左送中惡法<br />\n7.1 我地靠勇武 破壞左立法會<br />\n但你地諗下呢1個月黎 我地既運動除左打爛差館既窗 同拆左部份建築物之外 仲有咩既得益?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n就算俾我地攻入曬全港既警署又有咩得著 ?  但我地付出既會係大量既人命傷亡 中立既市民會反感<br />\n<br />\n我自已好多次都有出黎遊行 發夢 亦都見識到今次香港人既團結同力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n方法就比唔到大家 自問唔係一個叻人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我相信如果keep住依家運動既方向係絕對會失敗<br />\n而後果係俾14年更加慘痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地可以話劉細良係鬼 係左膠 但全件事都係政治事件   政治事件就係要政治解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QOXpQIMihME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQOXpQIMihME&d=JGY83BSksxqOTSpEwQoHnb7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=0c87e852\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QOXpQIMihME</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後如果你睇到呢到仲未走既 我相信機場集會係一個好大既武器去攻擊政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我重申 : <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用核彈炸 我都唔撚割蔗呀屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"57f5df6466e457267a73544f4e9c27ac13bdf66c","tid":1424545,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:10:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54e01731b484e1d6a811b5320850a2162b12f4ac","tid":1424545,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:11:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e480902feb51616f40a4fe194b6200a52ada27e","tid":1424545,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"推"}]}